{"tid":105392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】麥齊光公開拍片支持曾俊華參選行政長官","createTime":"2017-02-03T00:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T15:59:43.000Z","uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"140762ab1f8d3541991d40ebe27cc2cff39a151a","tid":105392,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:17:04.000Z","msg":"John Tsang 曾俊華<br />\n30 分鐘前 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n【麥齊光 X 曾俊華 拍住上！】<br />\n【麥齊光 X 曾俊華 拍住上！】<br />\n<br />\n「海納百川，有容乃大。」是我深信的人生哲學，這不只是珍貴的中國傳統智慧，即使解作現時年輕一代的術語「絕不割席」，其實也異曲同工。<br />\n<br />\n今日，我的舊同事麥齊光願意支持我，在城市發展方面給予我寶貴的意見，我心存感激。他提出香港應由高速城市發展 (rapid growth)，轉向為重視質素提升 (quality development)，與我的理念不謀而合，他的寶貴意見，豐富了我將要發表的政綱。<br />\n<br />\nCK，謝謝你的支持！感謝你和我，和香港人一起拍住上！<br />\n<br />\n#JohnTsang2017 #同曾俊華拍住上 #香港GOODSHOW #麥齊光<br />\n<br />\n轉自John Tsang 曾俊華 競選 Facebook專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/johntsangpage/videos/1848366632102647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjohntsangpage%2Fvideos%2F1848366632102647&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6udr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ea49cdd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/johntsangpage/videos/1848366632102647</a>"},{"pid":"ef4339914fe57092cdcaf8e7542b34833d80d772","tid":105392,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46ece91ca1c6696b6370e94323678b842033f143","tid":105392,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:25:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31536657d3d9e563c2f6f9407ed14c921fa87b4e","tid":105392,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想翻閹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e224042303495e283fd374cbd2edea268a2e8a32","tid":105392,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T