me":"2017-02-03T00:45:04.000Z","msg":"絕不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3482128a9d9a172a13425312eb51ab203305e92d","tid":105392,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麥齊光明明係淋病舊馬仔，背叛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為當日唔撐佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暗黑兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n監躉走去支持人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似打甩晒，人地冇罪係身喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fd5cdb57e310cf50ad7e2f1e5797b13da15969","tid":105392,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"林鄭「愛將」麥齊光：曾是唯一在職官員為他寫求情信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f6157fd35f13f9a42ea4b10fc702eb207a059c","tid":105392,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T00:53:46.000Z","msg":"麥齊光轉馬房"},{"pid":"e3b48f76503f9627545f01d7a0c9f2d409b66203","tid":105392,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭「愛將」麥齊光：曾是唯一在職官員為他寫求情信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9963d454fae7220b546cfb103829b2c1fe3ce9","tid":105392,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"果時係689放料令佢落馬 換個位俾波叔"},{"pid":"77ba5f6567c7ed63e0d58dedf267d61a96660b19","tid":105392,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"林鄭插條針入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明知自己成舊屎咁, 曲線撐林鄭<br />\n<br />\n到選舉後期又爆幾單選舉團隊醜聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628cdcc6873568f2696f2aa6dda5dfce70e1941f","tid":105392,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果時係689放料令佢落馬 換個位俾波叔</blockquote><br />\n又似喎<br />\n當初一落就換件劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778c00148f3ed7fe6d898c83b941b1228df60414","tid":105392,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>果時係689放料令佢落馬 換個位俾波叔</blockquote><br />\n又似喎<br />\n當初一落就換件劏房波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果期成日傳之後淋病同689不和 因為整9佢頭馬<br />\n係佔中局外人論之後不明原因先聯成陣線"},{"pid":"6a37e789be14d6ae8451f93b7fc4b23dda5a9880","tid":105392,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麥齊光明明係淋病舊馬仔，背叛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為當日唔撐佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暗黑兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n監躉走去支持人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似打甩晒，人地冇罪係身喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n接受am730專訪　表態撐曾俊華　林鄭「愛將」麥齊光：曾是唯一在職官員為他寫求情信<br />\n<br />\n一直被外界視為林鄭月娥「愛將」的發展局前局長麥齊光，接受《am730》專訪時卻公開表態支持林鄭的特首選舉對手曾俊華。麥齊光對《am730》說，因早已應承曾俊華，並贊同其促進社會和諧的參選理念。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">麥齊光又提到，當年自己捲入涉嫌詐騙租金津貼案，一直得到曾俊華的關心，時任財政司長的曾俊華，更是唯一在職官員為他向法庭撰寫求情信。</span></strong>對於是否要因這段雪中送炭的經歷而要「報恩」，麥齊光回應說：「唔係，義氣仔女啱啲。」"},{"pid":"6188bd628dbcc7b199b017de4ce8234b908e0bca","tid":105392,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"最弊fb班黃絲咩都唔理 盲撐鬍鬚曾呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f7a542b124eebc13eb9f2633648ce753392cf3","tid":105392,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:30:00.000Z","msg":"報恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9b493b1c0ba1d2c014ef539c54824991851655","tid":105392,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"諗返波叔呢4年上位速度都幾驚人<br />\n<br />\n由立法會功能組別投票機器 忽然變局長 而家做埋司長"},{"pid":"c808a37853f3d8aa4758114629c7cbd69c0ea54e","tid":105392,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"估唔到淋病無幫呢位前下屬寫求情信<br />\n<br />\n岩岩俾人拉果陣個女人仲好似好傷心話唔信佢會犯法等等"},{"pid":"bfe5d2d32c0e25337a3d8ebed984835876b22d6f","tid":105392,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗返波叔呢4年上位速度都幾驚人<br />\n<br />\n由立法會功能組別投票機器 忽然變局長 而家做埋司長</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n刷惦老細鞋，人工幾級跳<br />\n<br />\n其他梁粉咩李家仁醫生都撈得好惦"},{"pid":"8468223e72248943f8812ff9bd67d00e737f088c","tid":105392,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暗黑兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n監躉走去支持人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似打甩晒，人地冇罪係身喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n接受am730專訪　表態撐曾俊華　林鄭「愛將」麥齊光：曾是唯一在職官員為他寫求情信<br />\n<br />\n一直被外界視為林鄭月娥「愛將」的發展局前局長麥齊光，接受《am730》專訪時卻公開表態支持林鄭的特首選舉對手曾俊華。麥齊光對《am730》說，因早已應承曾俊華，並贊同其促進社會和諧的參選理念。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">麥齊光又提到，當年自己捲入涉嫌詐騙租金津貼案，一直得到曾俊華的關心，時任財政司長的曾俊華，更是唯一在職官員為他向法庭撰寫求情信。</span></strong>對於是否要因這段雪中送炭的經歷而要「報恩」，麥齊光回應說：「唔係，義氣仔女啱啲。」</blockquote><br />\n曾：曾俊華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}